{"tid":1801822,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"張建宗坦言香港冇全面「西方民主」 惟享「真正及實質自由」","createTime":"2019-12-29T03:19:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-29T07:50:39.000Z","uid":130626,"like":10,"dislike":164,"uniUserReply":74,"replies":[{"pid":"f3914ef9e827fc8c02ea53cabb8658ab23b4b4cf","tid":1801822,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T03:19:10.000Z","msg":"政務司司長張建宗今早出席電台訪問節目《給香港的信》時指，香港社會、經濟及民生在過去半年遭到重創，但認為香港有傳統制度優勢及基本經濟實力，以及「一國兩制」的獨特優勢，只要堅毅沉着應對，定會走出逆境，再現光芒。他又在網誌中表示，港府正籌備成立「獨立檢討委員會」，將研究及破解深層次矛盾。又稱港府在新一年會致力修補社會撕裂，讓香港重回正軌。<br />\n<br />\n張建宗慨嘆暴力及破壞在過去半年多已成為常態，重申法治是香港的核心價值之一，又指任何堅持法治的國家或經濟體，都難以容忍蓄意和有組織的破壞及暴力行為。港府將由專家及社區領袖組成「獨立檢討委員會」，主責研究社會衝突成因及探討深層次矛盾，亦會提出建議。張又稱，監警會將於未來數周向特首提交首階段報告。港人五大訴求包括真正雙普選，惟政府始終沒有回應，張建宗在網誌中也沒有談及這問題，更坦言：「或許香港沒有西方民主的全面外貌，但事實上香港長久以來一直不折不扣地享有真正及實質的自由」。<br />\n<br />\n張又認為，香港今年面對嚴峻考驗，受到中美貿易磨擦及社會動盪雙重打擊，不少人都期望社會可以盡快恢復秩序，令經濟得以復蘇。張指香港有韌性及足智多謀，在市民共同努力下，有信心可令香港復元。港府亦推出四輪經濟紓困措施，雖未能解決經濟問題，但相信有助本港企業及市民維持生計。他又強調港府在中央高度關懷及全力支持下，會準確地緊守及全面貫徹「一國兩制」原則，推動香港前進。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zHdnmAY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzHdnmAY.png&h=799a0dfe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191229/60428074?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191229%2F60428074%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=9uLtkTaOKuy%2FgkD%2BHbzoNRvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=7d3b3f7a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191229%2F60428074%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=b7717b09\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191229/60428074?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"2b77377b97a131f3c11d2f7c913fe4c4114ab1fb","tid":1801822,"uid":82640,"like":64,"dislike":0,"score":64,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T03:20:07.000Z","msg":"依加冇，唔代表未來冇<br />\n依加未獨立，唔代表遲下唔獨立"},{"pid":"b89c1f77e800dff622b3d45c457de7a3b3ab4a95","tid":1801822,"uid":259674,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T03:20:10.000Z","msg":"so what<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c154828809be0aaada93bedeb0c623af18827a27","tid":1801822,"uid":21545,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T03:20:17.000Z","msg":"佢未食藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66a1b14467885ef4321d7aed8fb63d8a81ae7869","tid":1801822,"uid":284463,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T03:21:06.000Z","msg":"黃色經濟圈的障礙<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1801188\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1801188</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2523b51f200b1912fc788b34a0fbb6665e494f69","tid":1801822,"uid":191588,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T03:21:18.000Z","msg":"又中國特色？dllm"},{"pid":"1931a660688524b014cdddfa6b1c906d082ede30","tid":1801822,"uid":22974,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T03:21:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"304a5b4b683faf52f2e6921e63ba2acb38352011","tid":1801822,"uid":266503,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T03:21:30.000Z","msg":"現在連自由都受到壓迫"},{"pid":"48439b4cbfaf9fd9e194a3114ccd3abc9309286b","tid":1801822,"uid":2142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T03:22:15.000Z","msg":"9up"},{"pid":"11abdf5c85e4c08393bf6247371cb2