序，令經濟得以復蘇。張指香港有韌性及足智多謀，在市民共同努力下，有信心可令香港復元。港府亦推出四輪經濟紓困措施，雖未能解決經濟問題，但相信有助本港企業及市民維持生計。他又強調港府在中央高度關懷及全力支持下，會準確地緊守及全面貫徹「一國兩制」原則，推動香港前進。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zHdnmAY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzHdnmAY.png&h=799a0dfe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191229/60428074?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191229%2F60428074%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=9uLtkTaOKuy%2FgkD%2BHbzoNRvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=7d3b3f7a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191229%2F60428074%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=b7717b09\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191229/60428074?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T03:31:21.000Z","msg":"邊個「專家」同<br />\n「社會領袖」入所謂檢討委員會<br />\n邊個就係鬼"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T03:45:45.000Z","msg":"劉鳴偉嗰班垃圾 乜尻屎青年委員會主席 代表曬班90後00後講野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T03:46:13.000Z","msg":"自己都中年啦"},{"pid":"423ef9171069a7b3392eda6d1ae023b92cc1edb5","tid":1801822,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f3914ef9e827fc8c02ea53cabb8658ab23b4b4cf","tid":1801822,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T03:19:10.000Z","msg":"政務司司長張建宗今早出席電台訪問節目《給香港的信》時指，香港社會、經濟及民生在過去半年遭到重創，但認為香港有傳統制度優勢及基本經濟實力，以及「一國兩制」的獨特優勢，只要堅毅沉着應對，定會走出逆境，再現光芒。他又在網誌中表示，港